text: Kryazhevoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kryazhevinsky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 658 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km north-east from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Kryazhevoye
